cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.SC 

This paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category as it describes the architecture of a partial evaluator for an evolving algebra. It may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category as it discusses analysis and optimization techniques used in the partial evaluator. Additionally, it could be classified under Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) as it deals with algebraic structures. Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Symbolic Computation (cs.SC) are also possible sub-categories as they are related to the topics discussed in the paper.
